xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Unleash: Deal an attack which has <Num0>% increased accuracy and <Num1>% increased strength per <Num2>% of the special attack bar used. (<Num3>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 開放：残り必殺技バーの<Num2>%を使用するごとに命中率+<Num0>%、ダメージ+<Num1>%で攻撃。(<Num3>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Immolate: Fire a powerful spell with <Num0>% improved accuracy. Damage scales based upon magic level and can be increased with magic damage boosting equipment. Costs no runes to use. (<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 焼却：命中率+<Num0>%の強力な魔法を放つ。ダメージは使用者の魔法レベル、装備品のボーナスに応じて変化。ルーンは不要。（<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Invocate: Fire a powerful spell that restores your prayer points by <Num0>% of the damage dealt. Damage scales based upon magic level and can be increased with magic damage boosting equipment. Your prayer points can go above your level, to a maximum of <Num1>. Costs no runes to use. (<Num2>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 召喚：与ダメージの<Num0>%の祈力ポイントを回復する強力な魔法を放つ。ダメージは使用者の魔法レベル、装備品のボーナスに応じて変化。レベル以上の祈力ポイントまで回復可能、上限は<Num1>。ルーンは不要。(<Num2>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Eviscerate: Perform an attack with your true maximum hit and a <Num0>% accuracy bonus. (<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 殲滅：真の最大ダメージと<Num0>%の命中率ボーナスを持つ攻撃を行う。（<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Evoke: Perform an attack with double accuracy, with a guaranteed enchanted bolt activation rate on successful hit. (<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 呼び起こす： 命中率2倍の攻撃を行い、命中すると魔法付与のボルトの発動率が保証される。(<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Wrath of Amascut: Perform an attack with <Num0>% increased accuracy and <Num1>% increased damage, but with halved attack speed. If hit, the opponent will take <Num2>% increased damage for the next <Num3> seconds. This special attack can only be used within the Tombs of Amascut. (<Num4>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: アマスカットの怒り：命中率+<Num0>%、与ダメージ+<Num1>%、攻撃速度半減で攻撃。命中した場合、相手はその後<Num3>秒間、<Num2>%増加したダメージを受ける。この必殺技はアマスカットの墓でのみ発動可能。(<Num4>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Tumeken's Light: Sacrifice <Num0> prayer points to restore your hitpoints to <Num1>% above their maximum, cure all poison, restore all drained stats (except prayer) and fully restore your run energy. This special attack can only be used within the Tombs of Amascut. (<Num2>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: ツメケンの光：祈力ポイント<Num0>消費、体力を最大値の<Num1>%まで回復し、すべての毒を治し、全ての低下ステータス（祈りを除く）と走力を全回復。この必殺技はアマスカットの墓でのみ発動可能。(<Num2>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Swarm: Fire <Num0> times in quick succession, dealing reduced damage and inflicting poison. (<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 大群： 低下したダメージと毒を与える攻撃を<Num0>回放つ。（<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Bear Down: Perform an attack with double accuracy, dealing additional damage over time, draining your target's agility level and preventing them from running. (<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: ベアダウン：2倍の命中率で攻撃。追加で継続ダメージを与え、対象の運動神経レベルを下げ、走れなくする。(<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Condemn: Fire a powerful spell with increased accuracy and damage, lowering your target's magic and defence levels by up to <Num0>%. (<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 糾弾：命中率とダメージが増加した強力な魔法を放ち、対象の魔法力と防御力を最大<Num0>%低下させる。（<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Disrupt: Summon a powerful bolt of lightning that deals guaranteed magic damage based on your max hit. (<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 混乱：強力な稲妻で確実に最大与ダメージに応じた魔法ダメージを与える。(<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Celebrate: Perform an attack to leave the area feeling more festive. (<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 祝う：お祭り気分を盛り上げる攻撃を行う。(<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Behead: Consume all Soul Stacks, attacking with increased damage and accuracy per stack, and healing for <Num0> health per stack. (<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 斬首： すべてのソウルスタックを消費し、1スタックにつきダメージと命中率が増加、体力を<Num0>回復。（<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Pulverize: A crushing blow with <Num0>% bonus accuracy that will reduce your target's defence by <Num1>%. (<Num2>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 粉砕： 命中率+<Num0>%で敵を粉砕し、対象の守備力を<Num1>%低下させる。(<Num2>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Burning barrage: Attacks <Num0> times in quick succession, with a chance to burn the enemy on each hit. (<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: バーニング・バラージ：<Num0>回連続で攻撃し、確率で一撃ごとに敵を火傷させる。（<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Scorching shackles: A scorching shot with <Num0>% bonus accuracy that will bind and burn enemy demons for <Num1> seconds.) (<Num2>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 灼熱の足かせ：命中率+<Num0>%の矢を放ち、悪魔の敵を<Num1>秒間拘束し焼却する。 (<Num2>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Scatter ashes: Casts the highest available demonbane spell. If it kills a demon, it refunds its special attack energy cost, and reduces the next attack delay. (<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 灰を撒き散らす： 使用可能な最も強い悪魔殺し魔法を唱える。悪魔を倒した場合、必殺技エネルギーを消費分回復、次の攻撃までのクールタイムを減少。(<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Weaken: Temporarily drain your target's Attack, Strength and Defence by <Num0>%. Is three times as effective against demons. (<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 弱体化：敵の攻撃力・腕力・守備力を<Num0>%低下。悪魔に対して効力は３倍。（<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Division: Fire a powerful piercing blade that reduces the targets Defence by <Num0>% of their Magic Level. (<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: ディビジョン：対象の守備力を魔法レベルの<Num0>%減少させる強力な刃を放つ。（<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Break Shackles: Attack with increased accuracy and damage based on the duration of any binding spells affecting them and ending said effect. This special attack requires the full Frostmoon set to be worn. (<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 束縛からの開放：拘束呪文の効果時間に応じて命中率+とダメージ+で攻撃し、拘束効果を終了させる。発動条件：全ブルームーン装備を装着すること。(<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Blood infusion: Sacrifice <Num0>% of your current hp to deal an attack with <Num1>% increased accuracy and damage, with a guaranteed set effect activation on hit. This special attack requires the full Bloodrager set to be worn. (<Num2>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 血液注入：現体力の<Num0>%を犠牲に、命中率とダメージが<Num1>%増加した攻撃をする。発動条件：全ブラッドムーン装備を装着すること。(<Num2>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Eclipse: Attack with <Num0>% increased accuracy, consuming all remaining burn damage affecting the target and raising the max hit by that amount. This special attack requires the full Eclipse set to be worn. (<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 月食：命中率+<Num0>%で攻撃。対象に残っている燃焼ダメージをすべて消費し、最大ダメージをその分上げる。発動条件：全エクリプス装備を装着すること。（<Num1>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: mainTabs source: combatOptionsTab wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: Virulence: Instantly metabolize any poison you are suffering from to buff your next attack by that amount of damage. (<Num0>%)
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 病原性：自分が受けている毒を即座に代謝し、次の攻撃をダメージ分増加。(<Num0>%)
